What's new in Salsa 1.0 (Since 0.3)

===============================================================================

New Python methods:

- loadSimulation()

- readTipsyArray()

- getTime()

- saveSimulation()

- writeGroupArray()

- importData()

- getAttributeRangeGroup()

- createVectorAttribute()

- runLocalParticleGroupCode()

- reduceParticle()

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Other Python Changes:

- Better error handling

- A map-reduce infrastructure (see reduceParticle())

- Update to track changes in PythonCCS interface in charm++ 6.2

- Detect Python 2.5 and 2.6

- More python samples, including implementation of some Tipsy commands.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Rendering Changes:

- Volume rendering to improve interactive performance on GL capable machines.

